data.description: This nicely updated, mid-size ranch home w/splashes of color throughout offers 3 BR's, 2 Full BA, spacious living room, kitchen w/ample cabinetry, pantry & dining area, & 1-car, attached garage.  Hallway & bedrooms feature beautiful hardwood floors.  Main bath has been completely updated w/all new tub, tile surround, multi-head shower system, vanity, & tile flooring.  All new vinyl plank flooring in kitchen, & laundry area, which includes the 2nd bath (shower only).  Enjoy nice days on your 6X15 front deck.  Or, for more privacy, take in the nice weather evenings on the large concrete patio in the fully fenced, backyard.  With everything all on one floor, an attached garage, fenced backyard, & being cosmetically updated throughout, this move-in ready home offers many conveniences in an affordable price range!
